Package com.github.dylon.liblevenshtein.collection.dawg.factory

Interfaces and implementations of factory classes for building DAWG structures.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDawgFactory<Node extends IDawgNode<Node>,Dawg extends IDawg<Node>>
    Constructs instances of IDawgNode, optionally using an object pool.
    IDawgNodeFactory<NodeType extends IDawgNode<NodeType>>
    Builds nodes for use in DAWG structures.
    IPrefixFactory<DictionaryNode>
    Builds instances of Prefix.
    ITransitionFactory<NodeType extends IDawgNode<NodeType>>
    Builds transitions that link nodes together, connected by a character label.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DawgFactory
    Constructs DAWG instances.
    DawgNodeFactory
    Builds nodes for use in DAWG structures.
    PrefixFactory<DictionaryNode>
    Builds Prefixes that build the terms in a DAWG structure.
    TransitionFactory<NodeType extends IDawgNode<NodeType>>
    Builds Transitions that link nodes together, under character labels.
